OL,3,COne Battle After Another sweeps Oscars
OL,4,Cwith six awards, including best picture
OL,6,FOne Battle After Another has swept
OL,7,Fwith Oscars, winning six awards,
OL,8,Fincluding best picture, as Michael B
OL,9,FJordan and Jessie Buckley picked up
OL,10,Fbest actors.
OL,12,FThe ceremony on Sunday, which saw
OL,13,FSinners cinematographer Autumn Durald
OL,14,FArkapaw make Oscar history as the
OL,15,Ffirst female director of photography
OL,16,Fto win the award, was a triumph for
OL,17,FOne Battle After Another director Paul
OL,18,FThomas Anderson, one of Hollywood's
OL,19,Fmost prolific filmmakers who had never
OL,20,Fwon an Oscar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
