OL,3,COne Battle After Another sweeps Oscars
OL,4,Cwith six awards, including best picture
OL,6,FOn top of best film, One Battle After
OL,7,FAnother, picked up best director and
OL,8,Fbest adapted screenplay for Anderson,
OL,9,Fthe Oscars' first trophy for best
OL,10,Fcasting and best supporting actor for
OL,11,Fan absent Sean Penn.
OL,13,F"I wrote this movie for my kids to say
OL,14,Fsorry for the housekeeping mess that
OL,15,Fwe left in this world - we're handing
OL,16,Foff to them," said Anderson while
OL,17,Faccepting the screenplay trophy. "But
OL,18,Falso with the encouragement that they
OL,19,Fwill be the generation that hopefully
OL,20,Fbrings us some common sense and
OL,21,Fdecency."
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@MO]yD@bOU}D@IO]
