OL,3,COne Battle After Another sweeps Oscars
OL,4,Cwith six awards, including best picture
OL,6,FThe black comedy action thriller,
OL,7,Fheaded by Leonardo DiCaprio, was the
OL,8,Ffavourite to be the big winner of the
OL,9,Fnight, with DiCaprio himself losing
OL,10,Fout on best actor in favour of Jordan.
OL,12,FRyan Coogler's Jim Crow-set, blues-
OL,13,Fsoaked vampire tale Sinners, which
OL,14,Fcame in with a record 16 nominations,
OL,15,Fwas the other big winner of the night.
OL,17,FAccepting his prize for playing a dual
OL,18,Frole as twins in Sinners paid tribute
OL,19,Fto past black Oscar winners as he
OL,20,Fcollected his trophy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
