OL,3,COne Battle After Another sweeps Oscars
OL,4,Cwith six awards, including best picture
OL,6,FArkapaw was also the first Black
OL,7,Fperson to win for best cinematography.
OL,8,FOnly the fourth female cinematographer
OL,9,Fever nominated.
OL,11,F"I really want all the women in room
OL,12,Fto stand up," said Arkapaw. "Because I
OL,13,Fdon't feel like I get here without you
OL,14,Fguys."
