OL,3,COne Battle After Another sweeps Oscars
OL,4,Cwith six awards, including best picture
OL,6,FBuckley won best actress for her
OL,7,Fperformance as Agnes Shakespeare in
OL,8,FHamnet, making her the first Irish
OL,9,Fperformer to ever win in the category,
OL,10,Fwith her victory one of the only
OL,11,Ftriumphs that felt like a guarantee in
OL,12,Fa night of close-calls.
OL,14,FShe added: "It's Mother's Day in the
OL,15,FUK today, so I would like to dedicate
OL,16,Fthis to the beautiful chaos of a
OL,17,Fmother's heart."
OL,26,@vD@LOUyD@PO]
