OL,3,COne Battle After Another sweeps Oscars
OL,4,Cwith six awards, including best picture
OL,6,F"We all come from a lineage of women
OL,7,Fwho continue to create against all
OL,8,Fodds ` thank you for recognising me in
OL,9,Fthis role," she added.
OL,11,FAs expected, the Netflix sensation
OL,12,FKPop Demon Hunters, 2025's most-
OL,13,Fwatched film, won best animated
OL,14,Ffeature, as well as best song for
OL,15,FGolden.
OL,17,FKPop Demon Hunters became a cultural
OL,18,Fphenomenon and the streaming
OL,19,Fplatform's biggest hit. It has more
OL,20,Fthan 325 million views and counting,
OL,21,Fwith a sequel recently announced.
