OL,3,COne Battle After Another sweeps Oscars
OL,4,Cwith six awards, including best picture
OL,6,F"This is for Korea and Koreans
OL,7,Feverywhere," said co-director Maggie
OL,8,FKang.
OL,10,FAnother Netflix release, Guillermo del
OL,11,FToro's Frankenstein picked up three
OL,12,Fawards, for costume design, makeup and
OL,13,Fhairstyling and for production design.
