OL,3,COne Battle After Another sweeps Oscars
OL,4,Cwith six awards, including best picture
OL,6,FAmy Madigan won best supporting
OL,7,Factress for her performance in the
OL,8,Fhorror thriller Weapons, a win that
OL,9,Fcame 40 years after the 75-year-old
OL,10,Factor was first nominated, in 1986,
OL,11,Ffor Twice in a Lifetime. Letting out a
OL,12,Fgiant laugh as she hit the stage,
OL,13,FMadigan exclaimed, "This is great!"
OL,15,FThere was a dramatic moment when there
OL,16,Fwas a tie in the live action short
OL,17,Fcategory, which was won by both Two
OL,18,FPeople Exchanging Saliva and The
OL,19,FSingers.
OL,26,@uD@TOUuD@cO]
