OL,3,COne Battle After Another sweeps Oscars
OL,4,Cwith six awards, including best picture
OL,6,FAfter the winners left the stage, host
OL,7,FConan O'Brien congratulated them and
OL,8,Fsaid: "You just ruined 22 million
OL,9,FOscar pools."
OL,11,FIt is the first time since 2013 there
OL,12,Fhave been tied winners, when Skyfall
OL,13,Fand Zero Dark Thirty shared the sound
OL,14,Fediting award.
