OL,3,COne Battle After Another sweeps Oscars
OL,4,Cwith six awards, including best picture
OL,6,FMr. Nobody Against Putin, a film about
OL,7,Fa Russian primary schoolteacher who
OL,8,Fdocuments his students' indoctrination
OL,9,Fto support Russia's war with Ukraine,
OL,10,Fwon best documentary, while Norwegian
OL,11,Ffamily drama Sentimental Value won
OL,12,Fbest international film.
OL,14,FThe ceremony was hosted for the second
OL,15,Fyear in a row by comedian O'Brien, who
OL,16,Fopened the ceremony with an extended
OL,17,Fsketch dressed as Aunt Gladys, getting
OL,18,Fchased by children through scenes from
OL,19,Fthe films nominated for best picture.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
