OL,3,COne Battle After Another sweeps Oscars
OL,4,Cwith six awards, including best picture
OL,6,FO'Brien also acknowledged that these
OL,7,Fare "chaotic, frightening times",
OL,8,Fadding: "It's at moments like these
OL,9,Fthat I believe the Oscars are
OL,10,Fparticularly resonant."
